<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sponsorship - SPARK</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/global.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="header-content">
            <div class="brand-identity">
                <img src="/images/spark_logo.png" alt="SPARK Logo" class="header-logo">
                <a href="/" class="site-title" style="text-decoration: none;">SPARK</a>
            </div>
            <nav class="header-nav">
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/sponsorship" class="active">Sponsorship</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/showcase">Showcase</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="section-dark hero-small">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>PARTNER WITH SPARK</h1>
                <p>Support the next generation of innovators and engineers.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section-content-block" id="sponsorship-page-content">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Why Sponsor SPARK?</h2>
                <p>SPARK is at the forefront of hands-on learning at Michigan State University. By sponsoring us, you're not just supporting a club; you're investing in the future of engineering, innovation, and leadership. Our students gain invaluable practical experience, tackle real-world problems, and develop skills highly sought after in today's workforce.</p>
                <p>Your contribution directly fuels student projects, provides access to cutting-edge tools and materials, and enables us to host workshops and events that inspire and educate.</p>
                <ul class="light-bulb-list">
                    <li>Access to a diverse talent pool of motivated engineering and computer science students.</li>
                    <li>Brand visibility among the MSU student body and faculty.</li>
                    <li>Opportunity for direct engagement with student projects and innovation.</li>
                    <li>Investment in practical, project-based learning that complements academic curriculum.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section-content-block">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Our Valued Sponsors</h2>
                <p>We are actively seeking partnerships to fuel innovation at SPARK. Be the first to join our list of supporters!</p>

                <div class="sponsor-level-section">
                    <h3>Gold Sponsors</h3>
                    <div class="sponsor-logos-grid">
                        <p>No Gold Sponsors yet. Be the first!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="sponsor-level-section">
                    <h3>Silver Sponsors</h3>
                    <div class="sponsor-logos-grid">
                        <p>No Silver Sponsors yet. Be the first!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="sponsor-level-section">
                    <h3>Bronze Sponsors</h3>
                    <div class="sponsor-logos-grid">
                        <p>No Bronze Sponsors yet. Be the first!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="section-content-block section-tiers-background">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Our Sponsorship Tiers</h2>
                <p>Choose the level of partnership that best fits your goals:</p>

                <div class="sponsorship-tiers-grid">

                    <div class="sponsorship-tier-card">
                        <img src="/images/Sponsorship Levels/Bronze.png" alt="Bronze Medal" class="tier-medal-icon">
                        <h3>Bronze</h3>
                        <p class="tier-price">$100</p> <p>Ideal for emerging supporters looking to make a foundational impact.</p>
                        <div class="tier-divider"></div>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Logo on website</li>
                            <li>Social media recognition</li>
                            <li>Invitation to all SPARK events</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="sponsorship-tier-card">
                        <img src="/images/Sponsorship Levels/Silver.png" alt="Silver Medal" class="tier-medal-icon">
                        <h3>Silver</h3>
                        <p class="tier-price">$300</p> <p>For partners seeking more visibility and direct engagement with our community.</p>
                        <div class="tier-divider"></div>
                        <ul>
                            <li>All Bronze benefits</li>
                            <li>Logo placement on all club merchandise</li>
                            <li>Recruiting opportunity at club meeting</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="sponsorship-tier-card">
                        <img src="/images/Sponsorship Levels/Gold.png" alt="Gold Medal" class="tier-medal-icon">
                        <h3>Gold</h3>
                        <p class="tier-price">$500</p> <p>Our premium partnership for maximum impact and deep collaboration.</p>
                        <div class="tier-divider"></div>
                        <ul>
                            <li>All Silver benefits</li>
                            <li>Larger logo placement on all club merchandise</li>
                            <li>Table at semester's showcase</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section-content-block">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Ready to Partner?</h2>
                <p>For inquiries or to discuss a custom sponsorship package, please contact us at <a href="mailto:RSO.spark@msu.edu">RSO.spark@msu.edu</a>.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2025 SPARK. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>